My Ancestors

This file inspires from the package radmixture, which is an ancestors calculator tool comtaining public calculator data. But the package only provides unvisible and single results. This’s why I write the file to make a cut short to find your ancestor infomation visiblely.

This file fits for those people:

  • learn some things about R and Rmarkdown;

  • get personal gene data;

  • want to know more ancestors information in your gene

data import

reliable package

library(radmixture)
library(data.table)
library(ggplot2)
library(ggthemes)

calculator data
